        <item>
            <id>https://www.ithome.com/0/876/548.htm</id>
            <title>8838 元：联想拯救者 R9000P 笔记本补货，锐龙 9 8945HX + 满功耗 RTX 5070</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/876/548.htm</link>
